Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.59,0:13:08.55,Nói chuyện - Selector,W,0,0,0,,Chúng ta đang ở đâu thế này?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.23,0:13:10.89,Nói chuyện - Selector,L,0,0,0,,Bell-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:11.78,Nói chuyện - Selector,B,0,0,0,,Lili!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:12.70,Nói chuyện - Selector,B,0,0,0,,Welf!
